User->>API: Upload Resume + Job Description

API->>Workflow: Start Optimization Workflow

Workflow->>Planner: Analyze resume and JD

Planner->>Retriever: Request relevant resume context

Retriever-->>Planner: Return ranked context

Workflow->>Rewrite: Generate optimized sections

Rewrite->>LLM: Structured rewrite request

LLM-->>Rewrite: JSON response

Rewrite->>Guardrails: Validate AI output

Guardrails-->>Rewrite: Safe structured output

Rewrite->>Validator: Business validation

Validator-->>Rewrite: Approved changes

Rewrite->>ATS: Calculate ATS score

ATS-->>Rewrite: ATS report + recommendations

Rewrite->>DB: Save optimization metadata

Rewrite->>Storage: Store generated .tex and PDF

Workflow-->>API: Optimization completed

API-->>User: Optimized Resume + ATS Report + Diff